issue.title: To Do: Change start marker to repeat
issue.body: Use start marker as a repeat marker. For repeated tones, alternate between the tone and repeat. For non-repeated tones, the start marker shouldn’t be necessary. Approx. 2x increase in transfer speed.

issue.title: Mic doesn't work on web browsers
issue.body: Mic doesn't work on web browsers on iOS, as well as non-localhost pages. This may be due to a Chrome security measure that requires a secure connection (https) to be established first.

issue.title: Change printing method in fft.js
issue.body: It's weird and prints a bunch of times IIRC.
